<subSubSection pageId="24" pageNumber="23" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="24.[192,1441,419,1787]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[240,397,1507,1531]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name means “imitator” and refers to this species’ similarity to several other species, especially the preceding.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
