<typeStatus box="[1067,1177,1571,1595]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">holotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="24" pageNumber="23" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="24.[192,1441,419,1787]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[240,603,1603,1627]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Diagnosis and discussion.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Austin and Mielke" authorityYear="2008" box="[612,923,1603,1627]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Porphyrogenes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="simulator">
<emphasis box="[612,923,1603,1627]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Porphyrogenes simulator</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is another large and bright species. It is generally similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Austin and Mielke" authorityYear="2008" box="[447,616,1635,1659]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Porphyrogenes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="splendidus">
<emphasis box="[447,616,1635,1659]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">P. splendidus</emphasis>
