, but is smaller, vein Rs arises just before CuA 
<subScript attach="left" box="[1204,1213,1651,1666]" fontSize="6" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">2</subScript>
(well before on 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Austin and Mielke" authorityYear="2008" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Porphyrogenes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="splendidus">
